sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_radi_infoblox.InfobloxIntegration</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>Used to gather subnets from Infoblox and dynamically create range sets and schedules (if applicable) for Discovery</description><name>InfobloxIntegration</name><script><![CDATA[var InfobloxIntegration = Class.create();
InfobloxIntegration.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },
	
	gatherSubnets: function() {
		var mid;
		var user = gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.user');
		if(!user) {
			gs.error('Infobox Integration Error: x_radi_infoblox.user property is not set');
			return;
		}
		var pass = gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.password');
		if(!pass) {
			gs.error('Infobox Integration Error: x_radi_infoblox.password property is not set');
			return;
		}
		var url = gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.url');
		if(!url) {
			gs.error('Infobox Integration Error: x_radi_infoblox.url property is not set');
			return;
		}
		var location = gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.location_attribute');
		if(!location) {
			gs.error('Infobox Integration Error: x_radi_infoblox.location_attribute property is not set');
			return;
		}
		var query = gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.query');
		var useMID = (gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.use_mid_server').toString() == 'true');
		if(useMID) {
			mid = this._getMIDServer();
			if(mid == null) {
				gs.error('Infobox Integration Error: No mid found to execute infoblox query');
				return;
			}
		}
		var origEndpoint = url + '/wapi/v2.1/network?_return_as_object=1&_paging=1&_max_results=1000&_return_fields=extattrs,network';
		if(query) {
			origEndpoint += '&*fxn!=vz&*fxn!=wz&*zone!=pub&*zone!=ext';
		}
		var endpoint = origEndpoint;
		var done = false;
		var ipCount = 0;
		var sites = {};
		sites.unknown = {};
		sites.unknown.ips = 0;
		sites.unknown.subnets = [];
		while(!done) {
			var restMessage = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
			restMessage.setHttpMethod('get');
			restMessage.setEndpoint(endpoint);
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
			restMessage.setBasicAuth(user, pass);
			if(useMID) {
				restMessage.setMIDServer(mid);
			}
			restMessage.setEccParameter('skip_sensor', 'true');
			var response = restMessage.execute();
			if(response.haveError()) {
				gs.error('Infobox Integration Error: ' + response.getErrorMessage());
				return;
			}
			var responseBody = response.getBody();
			responseBody = JSON.parse(responseBody);
			for(var index in responseBody.result) {
				if(location in responseBody.result[index].extattrs) {
					if(responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value in sites) {
						if(sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value].subnets.indexOf(responseBody.result[index].network) == -1) {
							sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value].ips += 1;
							sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value].subnets.push(responseBody.result[index].network);
						}
					}
					else {
						sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value] = {};
						sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value].ips = 1;
						sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value].subnets = [];
						sites[responseBody.result[index].extattrs[location].value].subnets.push(responseBody.result[index].network);
					}
				}
				else {
					if(sites.unknown.subnets.indexOf(responseBody.result[index].network) == -1) {
						sites.unknown.ips += 1;
						sites.unknown.subnets.push(responseBody.result[index].network);
					}
				}
			}
			ipCount += responseBody.result.length;
			if('next_page_id' in responseBody) {
				endpoint = origEndpoint + '&_page_id=' + responseBody.next_page_id;
			}
			else {
				done = true;
				break;
			}
		}
		this._syncRangesAndSchedules(sites);
	},
	
	_getMIDServer: function() {
		var midFinder = new global.MIDServerFinder();
		midFinder.setCapabilities(['rest']);
		var mids = midFinder.getMIDServers();
		if(mids.length > 0) {
			return mids[0];
		}
		else {
			midFinder.setCapabilities(['all']);
			mids = midFinder.getMIDServers();
			if(mids.length > 0) {
				return mids[0];
			}
		}
		return null;
	},
	
	_syncRangesAndSchedules: function(sites) {
		var rangeSet;
		var rangeSetID;
		var rangeItem;
		var newRange;
		var rangesFound;
		var schedule;
		var scheduleID;
		var scheduleRange;
		var includeUnknown = (gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.include_unknown_locations').toString() == 'true');
		var createSchedule = (gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.create_discovery_schedule').toString() == 'true');
		var locationField = gs.getProperty('x_radi_infoblox.servicenow_location_field');
		for(var site in sites) {
			if(site == 'unknown' && !includeUnknown) {
				continue;
			}
			rangeSet = new GlideRecordSecure('discovery_range');
			if(rangeSet.get('x_radi_infoblox_infoblox_id', site)) {
				rangeSetID = rangeSet.sys_id;
				rangeSet.x_radi_infoblox_last_infoblox_update = new GlideDateTime();
				rangeSet.update();
				newRange = false;
			}
			else {
				rangeSet.initialize();
				if(site == 'unknown') {
					rangeSet.name = 'Unknown Locations';
				}
				else {
					rangeSet.name = site;
				}
				rangeSet.x_radi_infoblox_infoblox_id = site;
				rangeSet.x_radi_infoblox_last_infoblox_update = new GlideDateTime();
				rangeSetID = rangeSet.insert();
				newRange = true;
			}
			rangesFound = [];
			for(var index in sites[site].subnets) {
				rangeItem = new GlideRecordSecure('discovery_range_item');
				rangeItem.addQuery('summary', sites[site].subnets[index]);
				rangeItem.addQuery('parent', rangeSetID);
				rangeItem.query();
				if(!rangeItem.next()) {
					rangeItem.initialize();
					rangeItem.name = sites[site].subnets[index];
					rangeItem.type = 'IP Network';
					rangeItem.parent = rangeSetID;
					var subnetSplit = sites[site].subnets[index].toString().split('/');
					if(subnetSplit.length == 2) {
						rangeItem.network_ip = subnetSplit[0];
						rangeItem.netmask = subnetSplit[1];
						rangeItem.insert();
					}
				}
				rangesFound.push(sites[site].subnets[index]);
			}
			if(newRange) {
				if(!createSchedule) {
					continue;
				}
				schedule = new GlideRecordSecure('discovery_schedule');
				schedule.initialize();
				if(site == 'unknown') {
					schedule.name = 'Unknown Locations';
				}
				else {
					schedule.name = site;
				}
				if(locationField) {
					var locationGR = new GlideRecordSecure('cmn_location');
					if(locationGR.get(locationField, site)) {
						schedule.location = locationGR.sys_id;
					}
					else {
						gs.warn('Infoblox Integration Warning: No Location record found for site "' + site + '" matching on the "' + locationField + '" field');
					}
				}
				schedule.mid_select_method = 'auto_select';
				scheduleID = schedule.insert();
				
				scheduleRange = new GlideRecordSecure('discovery_schedule_range');
				scheduleRange.initialize();
				scheduleRange.dscheduler = scheduleID;
				scheduleRange.range = rangeSetID;
				scheduleRange.insert();
			}
			else {
				rangeItem = new GlideRecordSecure('discovery_range_item');
				rangeItem.addQuery('parent', rangeSetID);
				rangeItem.addQuery('summary', 'NOT IN', rangesFound);
				rangeItem.deleteMultiple();
			}
		}
	},

    type: 'InfobloxIntegration'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jon@rapdev.io</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-04-20 19:52:59</sys_created_on><sys_id>c8bdf98fdb2f64102ed422e64896191f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>14</sys_mod_count><sys_name>InfobloxIntegration</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Infoblox Integration" source="x_radi_infoblox">a79df18fdb2f64102ed422e648961985</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Infoblox Integration">a79df18fdb2f64102ed422e648961985</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_c8bdf98fdb2f64102ed422e64896191f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jon@rapdev.io</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-04-23 18:27:29</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
